OL,5, The Victims Commissioner for London has
OL,6, described the sentence handed down to  
OL,7, her stalker of 19 years as "an insult".
OL,9,FIn October Elliot Fogel, 47, was found 
OL,10,Fguilty for a sixth time of breaching a 
OL,11,Flifetime restraining order designed to 
OL,12,Fstop him contacting Claire Waxman.     
OL,14,FHe was given a 16-month sentence but   
OL,15,Fwas released immediately as he had     
OL,16,Fspent time in custody awaiting trial.  
OL,18,FThe Home Office said it takes its      
OL,19,Fresponse to stalking "extremely        
OL,20,Fseriously".                            
